---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="IT Security Solutions | Cyberfyx">
  <section style="padding-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 60px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items: center; gap: 4rem;">
        <div class="fade-up">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">IT Security Solutions</h1>
          <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary);">Cyberfyx brings robust capabilities in delivering scalable, end-to-end IT security services tailored for diverse industry needs. Our team comprises certified security professionals with hands-on experience across cloud, on-premise, and hybrid infrastructures. With proven execution in vulnerability management, compliance (ISO 27001, ISO 27701, ISO 22301 etc), endpoint protection, and red team operations, we serve clients ranging from startups to large enterprises. Backed by strong GRC expertise and strategic advisory support , Cyberfyx ensures organizations are both resilient and audit-ready. Our adaptable staffing and 24/7 support models ensure rapid response and long-term security program success.</p>
        
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="text-align: center; padding: 4rem;">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-server" style="font-size: 6rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <h2>Our <span class="text-gradient">Framework Expertise</span></h2>
        <p>Comprehensive support across global security and privacy standards</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        
        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 27001:2022</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Information Security Management System</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Establishes a risk-based security framework to protect information assets.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-primary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Cyberfyx enables full lifecycle support from policy creation to audit preparation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-lock" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 27701:2019</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Privacy Information Management System</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Extends ISO 27001 for data privacy governance aligned with global laws like GDPR.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>We help organizations manage personal data processing with accountability and transparency.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-building-shield" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 22301:2019</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Business Continuity Management System</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Ensures preparedness and resilience against business disruptions and disasters.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-primary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Cyberfyx supports BIA, continuity planning, and recovery drills for certification.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 20000-1:2018</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">IT Service Management System</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Sets global standards for delivering managed IT services effectively and efficiently.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Our experts implement ITSM processes aligned with business performance goals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-lock" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 27017 & 27018</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Cloud Security & Privacy Controls</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Provides cloud-specific guidance for security and personal data protection.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-primary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>We help cloud service providers and customers secure and govern cloud environments.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">ISO 42001</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI Management System</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">A new framework for responsible, secure, and transparent use of Artificial Intelligence.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Cyberfyx assists in aligning AI systems with ethical, legal, and risk-based standards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">CSA STAR</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Cloud Security Alliance Certification</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Recognized cloud security certification combining ISO 27001 with CSA controls.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-primary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>We guide SaaS, PaaS, and IaaS providers through gap analysis and self-assessments.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-car-side" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">TISAX</h3>
          </div>
          <h4 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Trusted Information Security Assessment Exchange</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Required by the automotive industry for secure handling of sensitive data.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="margin-right: 8px; color: var(--accent-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Cyberfyx helps suppliers prepare for TISAX through risk assessments and audit support.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="grid-column: 1 / -1; padding: 2.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <div>
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem;">Internal Audits & Assessments</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">Regular reviews to ensure ongoing compliance, effectiveness, and readiness.</p>
          </div>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-clipboard-check" style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--accent-primary); opacity: 0.5;"></i>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to All Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
